{"tid":1729472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 (2)","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T08:48:16.000Z","uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40be24a0103aa81e65586e0e7200b7fc4b2b8594","tid":1729472,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1206461\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1206461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n以下內容以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">警察機動部隊(PTU)</span></strong></span>為主<br />\n因為佢地主打<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人群管理，防暴</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n資料多數係wiki<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">行動基地:(但可以調派到其他警局)</span><br />\n港島總區：北角警署<br />\n東九龍總區：觀塘警署<br />\n西九龍總區：石硤尾報案中心暨西九龍機動部隊行動基地<br />\n新界南總區：新界南總區總部及行動基地<br />\n新界北總區：新界北總區總部<br />\n訓練及後備大隊：粉嶺警察機動部隊基地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地有咩裝備?<br />\n<br />\n警察機動部隊作為一支在暴動中身先士卒的部隊，每名出勤的人員皆有完善的防暴裝備，<span style=\"color: violet;\">每名警察機動部隊人員的隨身裝備共重達40磅</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">身體防具:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.)防暴盔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSoJP5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSoJP5U.jpg&h=95e298dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設有散熱網，並且可以抵擋腐蝕性液體，後頸位設有護片。<br />\n<br />\n2.)Avon SF10型防毒面具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hkW96r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hkW96r.jpg&h=01c611d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俗稱「豬嘴」，英國製造，具有完全隔絕催淚煙、沙林毒氣和氯氣等毒氣的功能。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具會事先放喺大腿上嘅袋<br />\n要嘅時候就會拎出嚟用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w67nmeq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw67nmeq.jpg&h=4d84273f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(示意圖)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果見到前線開始開袋戴面具/換上已戴上面具嘅警察<br />\n就要小心!請盡可能保護自己!<br />\n因為好快就會用催淚彈!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">但因為所有警察都有受過催淚彈同胡椒噴劑訓練<br />\n唔排除會直接嚟料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.)防暴服連同多用途防火背心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ERfGgt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ERfGgt.jpg&h=de364b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淺綠色衫就係防暴服(有抗火功能)<br />\n身上有少少唔同嘅綠色背心就係多用途防火背心<br />\n<br />\n4.)防割手套&amp;防暴手套&amp;防暴靴<br />\n冇咩等別<br />\n同地盤佬用嗰啲差唔多<br />\n靴底可以防尖刺<br />\n<br />\n5.)盔甲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8k8gSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8k8gSq.jpg&h=c91ee382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俗稱鐵甲威龍，由15件不同部件組成，淨重9磅，為處理持刀等兇暴性人群的個人防禦裝備。<br />\n呢套嘢一着齊就好大獲!<br />\n(今日已經見到有警察着護手同護腿)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武器/工具:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.)胡椒噴劑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4LoQkG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4LoQkG.jpg&h=f4a46d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(細)<br />\n射程2m<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZdUWUc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZdUWUc.jpg&h=8903573c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(大)<br />\n射程5m<br />\n<br />\n2.)大型胡椒噴劑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sE08gUv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsE08gUv.jpg&h=84531f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要搵人咩住行<br />\n好似睇戲啲噴火槍咁<br />\n射程可達20m<br />\n可以加入有色溶劑<br />\n16年時旺角首次出現<br />\n仲有款係黃色筒(暫時搵唔到圖)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.)胡椒球發射器<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/12/104311_3cbe4c29fcfc6dc6a5727a26058aa3bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F12%2F104311_3cbe4c29fcfc6dc6a5727a26058aa3bd.jpg&h=c60f2fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVbCUJ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVbCUJ7.jpg&h=7a95d962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡椒球打喺示威者到會爆開同散發出胡椒噴霧<br />\n由壓縮氣體推動發射<br />\n槍上腰豆型嘅東東係彈匣<br />\n目標準確度約在18米內<br />\n有效射程為約45米<br />\n配備指定彈匣可盛載多達450枚胡椒球<br />\n16年時旺角首次出現<br />\n<br />\n(以上兩枝新嘢由<span style=\"color: navy;\">速龍隊</span>使用)<br />\n<br />\n4.)催淚煙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTpwZcT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTpwZcT.jpg&h=cf6e538c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內含5粒催淚煙彈頭<br />\n施放距離為50至70米<br />\n以法德魯鎮暴槍發射(圖中長槍)<br />\n<br />\n5.)手擲式催淚煙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwfweMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwfweMZ.jpg&h=fd122106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內含有23粒催淚煙彈頭<br />\n施放距離為15米<br />\n<br />\n6.)伸縮警棍<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PVxiEfy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPVxiEfy.jpg&h=36f0762f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一般用<br />\n有時會係銀色<br />\n<br />\n7.)鎮暴用警棍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umKwZfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumKwZfM.jpg&h=d792becd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一枝成型<br />\n打中痛好多<br />\n<br />\n8.)圓盾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhnOg3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbhnOg3s.jpg&h=ee76d13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以單手拎起<br />\n進攻用<br />\n<br />\n9.)長盾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/12/110247_0cc90a58502dda28ff3e40a12c7564e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F12%2F110247_0cc90a58502dda28ff3e40a12c7564e8.jpg&h=9f6d890a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高約1.7m<br />\n左右可以互相鎖住構成盾牆<br />\n防守用"},{"pid":"b3f725b05bf3f3fd7760c96e6e129ee984f73923","tid":1729472,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30cb080ef5857cebddbfe72e9591c88fa537f3b1","tid":1729472,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91c46681e3ebc38ac95b74f7cd8d12adb8012583","tid":1729472,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30cb080ef5857cebddbfe72e9591c88fa537f3b1","tid":1729472,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"丫叉做膽，彈藥發揮創意"}]}